      "content": "oh wow okay i didn't realize it was that bad. i just thought since it's a natural herbal thing it would be a mild boost rather than something heavy. are you sure? i've read online that people use them together for mild cases all the time without problems. like, is it really a huge risk if i just take a small dose?",
